{"paging":{"is_end":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567202163/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=24\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567202163/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=22\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","totals":60},"data":[{"id":567693953,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/567693953","vote_count":0,"voting":false,"created_time":1546142889,"is_delete":false,"resource_type":"answer","content":"\u003cp\u003e谢谢告诉我多重集的概念。域的概念大概知道，这里为是表达一种意思，严格来讲确实不应这么用。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我的总体想法是沿着集合论构造加法和乘法的，这在集合论中都有严格定义。所以我说的就是集合论基础上导致的逻辑问题。不妨试着从集合论的系统出发，看看是不是存在这种矛盾。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这就是，集合论中某个集合内不允许存在相同元素，而我们可以将可以属于某个集合内的某个元素放置在集合论的运算符的两端。我认为这里是有问题的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e多重集，按照定义，不属于集合。因此多重集是不可以运用集合论中的运算符的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e初等数学中的加法和乘法，是否有严格定义，老实说没有具体研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e反过来想一想，为什么必须限制集合中元素不可重复，为什么不可以不重复，运算符是否可以定义在集合框架外。集合论的世界中不允许出现重复，凭什么可以拿出重复的集合进行运算？\u003c/p\u003e","author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"8e45364b3e363dc02e487c4ef94a64a1","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8e45364b3e363dc02e487c4ef94a64a1","name":"basicquant","headline":"量化交易研究爱好者。","gender":1,"avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-79c71c1bc63ea507b398923f03b1fb08_s.jpg","type":"people","user_type":"people","badge":[],"is_following":false,"is_followed":false}},"is_author":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"replies_count":2,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"d592d4c542152f9845f9f17dbdf5a2d5","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/d592d4c542152f9845f9f17dbdf5a2d5","name":"猹猹","headline":"声豚,